# :icon[request] Requests

## Query String Pane :icon[query]

Use this pane to specify query string parameters to be appended to the endpoint specifed in the [info pane](#info-pane).  Each entry has a **parameter** and **value**.

To add a new query string parameter, click on "+ ADD".  Fill in the value and hit the save (disk) icon.  To edit an entry, click on the edit (pencil) icon.  TO delet an entry, click on the delete (X) icon.
